              </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="59_13_211__subsec_2__para_b">
              <num>(b)</num>
              <content>
                <p>are dedicated credits for the commission.</p>
              </content>
            </paragraph>
          </subsection>
        </section>
